tool_description: Obtenir les codes postaux des villes marocaines
name: Moroccan ZIP Codes
title: Moroccan ZIP Codes

api_list.name: GET CODE
api_list.description: Obtenir le code postale d'une ville marocaine à partir de son nom
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://moroccan-zip-codes.p.rapidapi.com/GET_CODE/RABAT"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "moroccan-zip-codes.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
